0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1682e3eb5e5e9e4a2efdae2ffe2e6825ec6d4a9c","tid":1944213,"uid":196211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"反正都係政府比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申長者"},{"pid":"89c0d2ab83c4493d6870a26d53f3b005cf981aec","tid":1944213,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"可加可加機制"},{"pid":"ac91902ff647910739945b7ee2f1f3ad884366ad","tid":1944213,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"點解咁多年 <br />\n票價就係咁加加加 <br />\n<br />\n$2 特惠站 仲係 $2 ？"},{"pid":"b35ecdb69727543524fe178e8b45888e4615cde1","tid":1944213,"uid":143727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"其實自從有左巴士月票真係唔再搭港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n年年加價剝削香港人，亞洲國家中香港都所算貴地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}